## ðŸ’¡ Tips for Success
1. **Contests are king** â€” You get better faster by competing, then upsolving.
2. **Track progress** â€” Use [StopStalk](https://www.stopstalk.com/) or a spreadsheet.
3. **Don't chase rating early** â€” Focus on problem-solving depth.
4. **Analyse before learning** â€” Struggle for 30-60 min before reading editorial.
5. **Speed practice** â€” Occasionally solve 5-10 easy problems in 1 hour to boost speed.
6. **Math is your friend** â€” CP loves number theory & combinatorics.
7. **Mixed practice** â€” Interview-style + CP problems to avoid tunnel vision.

